text: Ichsan PratamaIchsan ligaindonesia (born, 18 January 1992) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a central midfielder for Liga 2 club PSIM Yogyakarta. ==Career== ===Barito Putera=== Ichsan joined in the squad for the 2016 Indonesia Soccer Championship A.
